{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledged"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledged\/delay"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh29GenericOnOffSetUnacknowledgedV5delays5UInt8VSgvp","title":"delay","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identi